snippet.title: Is Johnny Depp an abuser to or victim of abuse by Amber Heard? (AN Hot Takes)
snippet.description:
#justiceforjohnnydepp #metoo

This is an odd one and, while I can't definitively say that Johnny Depp is not an abuser, I CAN definitively say that he is a victim of abuse, per Amber Heard's own statements. 

As important as the #metoo movement has been in exposing abusive men, these cases keep popping up of women lying in order to ruin innocent men. Every time that happens, it only serves to destroy credibility of honest women who are victims. 

I don't know for sure if Depp was abusive, but two wrongs still don't make a right and we do know for sure that Heard was abusive and a liar. 

Question Everything. Stay Uncomfortable.
Let’s get weird!
